reviewText:
It is a good game, you will have fun with it.
Pros:
Different fight styles as pure combat, stealth renegade and technomancer;
Intriguing story with a choice of which side to play the last chapter;
a little romance, you can choose between 3 ladies, but as I said it is a little;
Dialogs that you can choose answers that influence the game;
Great art and gorgeously rendered;
Cons:
Some of the answers are not clear as positive or negative, so it is hard to understand if you are being good or bad;
The story shows the bad side of your choices, so there is no good side, just bad and bad;
Just a few weapons and armors;

Pros:
- Combat system is really nice... and thats all.

Cons:
- Crafting is mostly about nothing;
- Not much weapon and armor types;
- Most locations are corridor" like;
- You can only interact with quests related NPCs and traders;
- Boring loot;
- The world is like static

